                            <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> vnd der
                            <expan>Judıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey vns wonhaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l7">etc Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe ſache do </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l8">Jr vns vormals <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch
                                <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / von
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> notdurft <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        ver </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l9"><expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> . mıt
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> brıef / des
                            <expan>datu<ex>m</ex></expan> hellt am montag vor ſand Margreten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l10">tag <expan>nehſtu<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> /
                        Darinn eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> hat wıe
                                <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l11">ſache bıs auf <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ʒeıt
                        gehandelt ıſt vnd daʒ wır redlıch vnd vngeuer = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l12">lıch da mıt <expan>vmbgange<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeın .
                        So ıſt vns <expan>ſeıth<ex>er</ex></expan> von dem
                            <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l13"><expan>tıgıſte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sıg<ex>munden</ex></expan>
<expan>Römıſch<ex>e</ex>m</expan> ʒu <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd ʒu
                        Beheım </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l14">etc künıg <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> eın brıef <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l15">brıefs <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> Jnnhelltt daʒ
                        wır dıe <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey vns weıſen
                                <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l16"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>Burggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> gnug ʒutun nach lawt ſeinr
                                <expan>künıglıche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l17"><expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gegeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd als er das
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . <expan>Marggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l18"><expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> ʒu
                                <expan>entſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> hab . / Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wır getan vnd <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l19">von der <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey vns <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . <expan>Marggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l20">durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rate
                        vnd dıe <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey vns . für ſıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l21">ſelbs ʒu <expan>menig<ex>er</ex>m</expan> mal fleıſſıg
                                <expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan> . dıe
                                <expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>n<ex>te</ex></expan> ſache
                                <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l22"><expan>Burggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>
<expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd der <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan>
                        bey vns ʒu <expan>entſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> nach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l23">lawt des <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> .
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedıgıſte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des künıgs brıef .
                            <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> vnſerm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l24"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem
                                <expan>Marggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> geſant / Des wır hoffen daʒ der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l25"><expan>gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . der <expan>Marggr<ex>af</ex></expan> wol
                        eingedenk ſüll ſein . So <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l26"><expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey vns des vor
                                <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Marggr<ex>af</ex></expan> noch
                        alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l27"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu awſʒtrag
