<expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> mıt fleıſſ darcʒu tun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l28">Dabey eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vnd
                                <expan>menikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mag daʒ dıe
                            <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l29">nıht <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>ſecʒıg</expan> noch
                                <expan>vngehorſa<ex>m</ex></expan> vnd der ſache nach
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedıgıſte<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l30"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des künıgs geheıſſ ʒu
                        awſʒtrag ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . nıht ſeẅmıg
                                <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
<pb facs="#facs_69" id="33v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_69_r1l1">ſein noch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd auch noch nıht ſeẅmıg ſein noch
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒıehen</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_69_r1l2"><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / ſo
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır dem
                            <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Burggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>vnd<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dınge<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_69_r1l3">neẅlıch aber <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> / Ob
                        ſein gnade deẅht daʒ wır in den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> ıcht
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_69_r1l4">getan <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gelaſſ<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> denn wır pılleıch
                            <expan>ſölte<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ wır <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_69_r1l5"><expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſein <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> an den
                                <expan>ſtette<ex>n</ex></expan> da wır das denn
