<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>marggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, zu
